## 4) Goals & Non-Goals
**Primary Goals**
- Increase **demo sign-ups** via prominent CTAs and smooth booking flow.
- Educate visitors on **what each Bee does** and the value vs. manual work.
- Establish **brand credibility** with testimonials and concise benefit proofs.

**Non-Goals (MVP)**
- No full app beyond landing + lead capture.
- No live AI demos inside the page.
- No multi-language or multi-region rollout (yet).

**Near-term Consideration**
- Structure content so **new Bees** can be added easily (admin configurable).

**Bees in MVP**
- **Social Bee** (automates social media)
- **Sales Bee** (automates sales outreach; phrase: ‚ÄúBook meetings‚Äù not ‚ÄúClose deals‚Äù)
- **Bespoke Bee** (custom requirements; quote after intake)

All flows must **capture lead details** and push to **Cal.com** with prefilled info.

