## 8) Architecture Overview (Tech Stack)
- **Frontend:** Next.js (App Router, TypeScript), Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, light Framer Motion animations.
- **Auth:** Clerk (Admin area only).
- **Backend:** Next.js Route Handlers (`/api/*`).
- **DB/ORM:** PostgreSQL + Prisma.
- **Email:** Resend (lead follow-ups and internal alerts).
- **Scheduling:** Cal.com embed/overlay (prefill lead data via query params).
- **Infra/Deploy:** Vercel.
- **Config:** Environment variables for Clerk, DB, Resend, Cal links.

